These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, salsa
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | tea |
| Hobby         | drawing  | sudoku       |
| Job           | mechanic   | freelancer    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | zombie   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | pop     |
| Sport         | basketball | tennis      |
| Transport     | tram       | airplane           |

