.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: apple, asparagus
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, firefighter
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, italian
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, motorbike
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is on the left of the fisherman##1
5. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda         | fanta       |
| Food          | apple        | asparagus |
| Job           | firefighter | fisherman    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | zombie  |
| Nationality   | italian        | dutch       |
| Pet           | snake            | hedgehog        |
| Transport     | motorbike            | bike       |

