The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, ship
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the project-manager is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
5. the project-manager is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
