.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, disco
2 different pets are kept: horse, goat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, roller
1. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching romance movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice    | fanta   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | romance     |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | dubstep        |
| Pet           | horse        | goat |
| Sport         | skiing    | biathlon |
| Transport     | roller         | bus       |

